title: Week 10 NFL Recap, Analysis; Kirk Cousins wins in primetime (Football 11/11)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Ryan Wilson, John Breech and Sean Wagner-McGough to recap all the Week 10 action from around the NFL. The guys discuss all 11 games on the Sunday slate including Vikings-Cowboys (1:30), Chiefs-Titans (14:40), Ravens-Bengals (25:30), Bills-Browns (31:55), Lions-Bears (42:30), Panthers-Packers (47:00), Falcons-Saints (54:45), Dolphins-Colts (58:45), Rams-Steelers (1:05:45), Cardinals-Bucs (1:14:30) and Giants-Jets (1:20:00).
